
============
Contributing
============

The ``superset-sup`` project (formerly ``preset-cli``) is licensed under the Business Source License 1.1.
If you would like to contribute to the project, and you are not a member of the core development team
or a contributor with write access to the repository, you will be given the option
to sign a Contributor License Agreement (CLA) when you submit any pull requests.

Issue Reports
=============

If you experience bugs or general issues with ``superset-sup`` (including the legacy ``preset-cli``
and ``superset-cli`` commands), please report them on
`GitHub Issues <https://github.com/preset-io/superset-sup/issues>`_ or the
`Preset Support Portal <https://preset.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/1/group/1/create/1>`_.
